d einen neuen Herrschaftskonsens stiften.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 30. Aug 2021) 0aCommunismxHistory. 0aIdeologyxHistory. 0aPost-communismxHistory. 0aSocialismxHistory. 0aUtopiasxHistory. 7aHISTORY / Russia & the Former Soviet Union.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2016z9783110485103oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2016z9783110485189oZDB-23-DEG40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783412506490423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783412506490.jpg  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DEGb2016  aZDB-23-DGGb2016